headline: KeyBanc bullish on Booking as AI and scale to drive growth
summary: Investing.com --KeyBanc started coverage of Booking Holdings with an Overweight rating and a $6450 price target on company’s global scale, and industry leading margins. It started Expedia and Airbnb, maintaining a Sector Weight view on both.
